{"tid":243710,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"利記應唔應該賣史杜列治","createTime":"2017-05-14T23:25:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-16T21:43:08.000Z","uid":28802,"like":8,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"60dbcd4606447cfc7b3b7e8aba1f6e1c876ec471","tid":243710,"uid":28802,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T23:25:06.000Z","msg":"史杜先27歲<br />\n14年踢國家隊大傷之後呢三年係咁傷<br />\n真係睇到好傷心<br />\n其實都係咁傳話會出走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然今次復出即刻入波<br />\n但當年21球真係成絕響<br />\n<br />\n大家覺得應唔應賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 完了吧 如無意外<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  </span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 留呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span><br />\n<br />\n傷患報告：<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/15/072437_ca87b22db26f97dc5f6eca7b38a4150a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F15%2F072437_ca87b22db26f97dc5f6eca7b38a4150a.jpg&h=d0dbdbf8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"90247d07ba4ae93412308265bd49d6774425eecf","tid":243710,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T23:26:42.000Z","msg":"應唔應該有得你渣主意咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce1d95267af6533aa84d9b342d01a41a2ac5a431","tid":243710,"uid":28802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T23:27:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>應唔應該有得你渣主意咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n討論下啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fea334fdbcbbd177b31e7c7aa1d